name: ESGO 2017 Congress: 20th Biennial International Meeting of the European Society of Gynaecological Oncology
content: The European Society of Gynaecological Oncology (ESGO) reveals the latest clinical and research developments in Gynaecological Cancers treatment and care at ESGO 2017 Congress, Europe's landmark meeting on Gynaecological Oncology, Nov 04-07, Vienna, Austria.
